headline: GoDaddy Inc. to Announce Second Quarter 2025 Financial Results on Thursday, August 7, 2025
summary: GoDaddy Inc. (NYSE: GDDY) will release financial results for the second quarter of 2025 on Thursday, August 7, 2025, after the U.S. stock market closes.

headline: Security Double Standard? Young Consumers Reuse Passwords, Expect Businesses to Be Fort Knox
summary: A new GoDaddy (NYSE: GDDY) survey reveals a surprising paradox among younger consumers: while Gen Z and Millennials appear less concerned about protecting themselves online, they have little tolerance for businesses that fall short on security.
